Idalmis S. OLIVERA, Appellant,
v.
PUBLIX SUPER MARKETS, INC., Appellee. No. 3D18-784 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. Opinion filed September 5, 2018 Idalmis S. Olivera, in proper person. Weiss Serota Helfman Cole & Bierman, P.L., and Edward G. Guedes, Coral Gables and Richard B. Rosengarten, for appellee. Before SUAREZ, SCALES and LUCK, JJ. PER CURIAM.

Affirmed. See Walker v. Winn-Dixie Stores, Inc. , 160 So.3d 909 , 912-13 (Fla. 1st DCA 2014) ; Gaidymowicz v. Winn-Dixie Stores, Inc. , 371 So.2d 212 , 214 (Fla. 3d DCA 1979).
